<title>USA: Portec sets first payout since 1986.</title>
<headline>Portec sets first payout since 1986.</headline>
<dateline>LAKE FOREST, Ill. 1996-10-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Portec Inc said Tuesday it will pay a quarterly cash dividend for the first time since 1986.</p>
<p>The company said it will pay $0.08 a share on December 16 to shareholders of record November 11.</p>
<p>Portec undertook a major restructuring after its last dividend, the company said, cutting bank debt and raising shareholder equity.</p>
<p>--Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787</p>
